{{Hot spring in Japan | name = Yoshinoike Onsen (葭之池温泉) | image = | caption = | location = {{ill|Yamanashi Prefecture|ja|山梨県|12=draft}} {{ill|Fujiyoshida|ja|富士吉田市|12=draft}} | access = Train: 1-minute walk from {{ill|Yoshiike Onsen-mae Station|ja|葭池温泉前駅|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Fujikyuko Line|ja|富士山麓電気鉄道富士急行線|12=draft}}. | spring_type = {{ill|Simple hot spring|ja|単純温泉|1=Simple Hot Springs|12=draft}} | spring_temperature = | discharge = | pH = | water_type = | osmotic_pressure = | lodging = 1 facility | capacity = | annual_visitors = | year = | website = | notes = }}
'''Yoshinoike Onsen''' (葭之池温泉) is a {{ill|hot spring|ja|温泉|1=Onsen|1=Onsen|12=draft}} located in {{ill|Fujiyoshida|ja|富士吉田市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Yamanashi Prefecture|ja|山梨県|12=draft}} (formerly part of {{ill|Kai Province|ja|甲斐国|12=draft}}), Japan.
== Spring Quality == * {{ill|Simple hot spring|ja|単純温泉|1=Simple Hot Springs|12=draft}} (cold mineral spring)
== Onsen Area == [[File:Yosinoike.jpg|thumb|Yoshinoike Onsen and the nearby Yoshinoike Pond, which inspired the name]] The onsen area is located on the outskirts of Fujiyoshida city and features one day-use hot spring facility, also named "Yoshinoike Onsen." The facility's main building is a traditional thatched-roof structure.
The baths consist of separate indoor facilities for men and women. The attached restaurant serves {{ill|Yoshida Udon|ja|吉田のうどん|12=draft}}.
== History == [[File:FujisanSimomiyaOmuroSengenShrine Kayu-ura Ritual.jpg|thumb|The Kayu-ura Ritual performed annually at {{ill|Fujisan Shimomiya Omuro Sengen Shrine|ja|冨士山下宮小室浅間神社|12=draft}} by the Yoshinoike Onsen family]] Yoshinoike Onsen was founded in {{ill|1856|ja|1856年|12=draft}} ({{ill|Ansei era|ja|安政|12=draft}} 3). It operated as a ryokan until the prewar era and underwent renovations in 1989 (Heisei 1).
== Access == * '''Train''': 1-minute walk from {{ill|Yoshiike Onsen-mae Station|ja|葭池温泉前駅|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Fujikyuko Line|ja|富士山麓電気鉄道富士急行線|12=draft}}. * '''Car''': ** About 12 minutes from {{ill|Kawaguchiko Interchange|ja|河口湖インターチェンジ|12=draft}} or about 5 minutes from {{ill|Fujiyoshida Nishikatsura Smart Interchange|ja|富士吉田西桂スマートインターチェンジ|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Chuo Expressway|ja|中央自動車道|12=draft}}. ** About 12 minutes from {{ill|Fujiyoshida Interchange|ja|富士吉田インターチェンジ|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Higashi-Fujigoko Road|ja|東富士五湖道路|12=draft}}.
